Porto Beats Villarreal 5-1 in Europa League Semis; Benfica Tops Braga 2-1

-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 
2011-04-28T21:00:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-28/porto-beats-villarreal-5-1-in-europa-league-semis-benfica-tops-braga-2-1.html
Porto beat Villarreal 5-1 and
Benfica defeated Braga 2-1 to open the semifinals in soccer’s
Europa League.  Radamel Falcao scored four goals to lead Porto, while
second-half goals from Jardel and Oscar Cardozo gave Benfica the
victory.  Villarreal and Braga will host the return matches in the
two-game series on May 5. The final of  Europe ’s second-tier club
competition will be played May 18 in Dublin.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  